=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有乜可能可以刑責同犯嘅罪可以唔相稱到呢個地步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:18:23.000Z","msg":"又用晒 CAAR4-CAAR6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:23:16.000Z","msg":"分分鐘今日單堵路上訴都會用<br />\n跟住話刑期仲有上調空間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:36:14.000Z","msg":"堵路就直接用非法集結告啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"521089eb93f679136e978bc8146bd7d6419b3cc6","tid":2418842,"uid":105802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:40:51.000Z","msg":"-<br />\n家棟最終被判八個月刑期，即時監禁。<br />\n<br />\n但家棟的伙伴們仍會繼續照顧牆內的手足及家人。<br />\n<br />\n旁聽資訊仍會持續更新。<br />\n<br />\n好人一生平安。<br />\n<br />\n請大家繼續支持囚權工作。<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n家棟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/108296297598557/posts/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F108296297598557%2Fposts%2F&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XoL97yTsFD7TFgzLZRxFgWk%3D&h=f8ad4ca3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/108296297598557/posts/</a><br />\n250345976726921/?d=n"}],"pinned":{"pid":"780764a59fce572e44b402901e4535af34392e14","tid":2418842,"uid":22556,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T02:46:15.000Z","msg":"「社工復興運動」劉家棟在前年7.27元朗大遊行中，高舉社工證呼籲警方防線減慢推進以給予示威者時間離開，去年6月被裁定阻差辦公罪成，裁判官在未有索取任何背景報告的情況下，即時宣判監禁一年，惹來社福界嘩然。劉之後獲准保釋等候上訴，法官黃崇厚今（23日）在高等法院宣布定罪上訴遭駁回，刑期則由12個月減至8個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.